## How to Run

### Backend
```bash
cd backend
npm install
# Ensure .env has valid MONGO_URI
npm start
# For verification: node verify_api.js
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
# Open http://localhost:5173
```

### AI Service
```bash
cd ai-budget-assistant
python app.py
```

